content:
The Insurance Policyholder Portal is a self-service portal that allows policyholders to manage their insurance accounts. They can access policy details, review coverage options, submit claims, and track claim progress from their devices. The portal offers transparency and efficiency in managing insurance matters.

Available in Lightning Experience in Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions with FSC Insurance add-on enabled.

The portal includes:

* Portal Home Page: a summary of policies
* My Policies Page: a list view of policies
* Policy Record Page: policy details for each policy
* My Claims Page: a list view of claim records
* Claim Record Page: claim details for each claim

Set up the Insurance Policyholder Portal by performing tasks on these pages.
title: Policyholder Insurance Portal
